	Version 2.1 (2021-04-07) by JOTD:
    - jump with second button
    - level & sublevel select (issue #0005041)
    - full joypad controls
    - trainer: infinite lives/time/extras
    - BUTTONWAIT allows to see intro picture
    - fixed typos in the manual
    
	Version 2.0 (2016-01-09) by Wepl:
	- overall rework
	- support for CDTV/AmigaFun version added
	- random generator moved to fast memory
	- faster blitter fixes
	- sp moved to fast memory
	- several speedups
	- new install script/imager
	
 - CUSTOM2=1: jump using second/blue button, smart bomb uses green CD32 button.
 - CUSTOM1: trainer: infinite lives, time, smart & super smart bombs (hiscores won't be saved).
 - adapted to whdload v17

 - CD32 joypad controls:
   * play=pause
   * reverse+forward=quit
   * reverse+forward+yellow=quit to wb
   * blue: jump (if CUSTOM2 is set)
   * green: flash (if CUSTOM2 is set, else it's blue)
   * yellow: grenade
   * down+blue/green (depending on CUSTOM2): gyroscope
